
'''= GoodEnoughCNC: Affordable & useful open source CNC machines'''

URL = http://goodenoughcnc.eu

=Description=

[[DiDIY]]:

"GoodEnoughCNC is a very low-cost CNC mill built from standard
mechanical components and steel profiles. Just basic hand tools are
needed for its assembly. It is a hybrid and can be transformed from CNC
mill into various other digital fabrication tools, such as a plasma cutter,
spindle or laser cutter. It is modular and fully Open Source Hardware."
(http://www.didiy.eu/public/deliverables/didiy-d6.3-1.0-pub.pdf)



